CustomField.description:
Row and column headers for each of the tables in the giving details tab. The form is:
{
"giving_totals":{"columns":["col1","col2"], "rows": ["row1","row2"]},
"pledge_recurring":{"columns":["col1","col2","col3"], "rows": ["row1","row2","row3"]},
"pledges":{"columns":["col1","col2","col3"], "rows": ["row1","row2","row3"]},
"pledge_payments":{"columns":["col1","col2","col3"], "rows": ["row1","row2","row3"]},
"gifts":{"columns":["col1","col2","col3"], "rows": ["row1","row2","row3"]}
}

If any tables are not defined by this object it will use the defaults instead.
